{"word":"ἀμοιβός","slug":"ἀμοιβός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμοιβός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀμείβω'><el>ἀμείβω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>one who exchanges</i>, <el>ἀμοιβοί</el> <i>soldiers that relieve others</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a> <i>in return</i> or <i>in exchange for</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}